This is a Gentoo overlay for stuff we use or make at Kozea.

To use use it, create the file /etc/portage/repos.conf/kozea.conf
    [kozea]
    location = /var/lib/portage/repos/kozea
    sync-type = git
    sync-uri = https://github.com/Kozea/Overlay.git
    auto-sync = yes

Then synchronize the repositories and add the kozea overlay
    emaint sync -r kozea

See the Gentoo documentation for details:
    http://www.gentoo.org/proj/en/overlays/userguide.xml
